profile:
Green Side Up Contracting Inc. is a professional member of Landscape Ontario & we are an authorized TrexPro - Platinum status!

Over the last 22 years, we have established ourselves within the construction industry as an honest and reputable contractor.  We have earned this reputation by shaping the company around four core values: honesty, transparency, quality of workmanship, backed by above industry-standard warranties!

As the President of Green Side Up Contracting Inc. and a board member of the Toronto Chapter of Landscape Ontario, PROTECTING YOUR INVESTMENT and delivering EXCELLENCE are two of Jay's key priorities.

         ****************************10 YEAR STRUCTURAL WARRANTY - FENCING ****************************

Green Side Up Contracting Inc is a consistent award-winning, construction company that focuses on delivering high-quality workmanship and superior customer service.  We put our trust into our clients with extremely favorable payment terms - pay when the job is completed! We are active members of our community and believe in helping those who are less fortunate.

Services provided include but are not limited to:

-> Fence Construction (80' linear feet minumum)
 
-> Interlocking & Landscape Construction

-> Deck Construction (200 sq foot minumim) 

    - Trex
    - Cedar

***

Not only does Green Side Up Contracting Inc focus on PROTECTING YOUR INVESTMENT by offering a TEN-YEAR structural WARRANTY on fencing, we also believe that doing business together should be simple and transparent.

***

Please use our SELF SERVE CALCULATORS to obtain an INSTANT ESTIMATE for your DECK, FENCE or INTERLOCK project:

FENCE CALCULATOR: https://greensideupcontracting.com/fence-building-calculator/

DECK CALCULATOR: https://greensideupcontracting.com/deck-calculator/

INTERLOCKING CALCULATOR: https://greensideupcontracting.com/interlock-cost-calculator/

***

Please be sure to check our work by visiting:

Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/greensideupcontracting/

YouTube: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCRNuc7PofUOEHCwMf7NdUzQ/videos?view_as=subscriber

Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/GreenSideUpContracting/

We would also invite you to come on site during the construction process, so you can see our work in progress!

***

Building is fun, business is great, people are terrific and life is wonderful! 

I ask that you put your trust into Green Side Up Contracting - we not disappoint!!

On your side,

Jay Saveall

www.greensideupcontracting.com

profile:
We are Action Home Services, and we always take action for every construction service that you need. Based in Toronto, Ontario, we are a general contracting company that specializes in a wide range of services. We will help you to design and build an outside living area of your dream. Do not wait! Take action with Action Home Services. Check our website at http://actionhomeservices.ca/ to find out more. 

Our Mission
We aim to become one of the most successful construction companies within Toronto, Ontario. This mission will not happen if our services are not up to the level of what our customers are expecting. Thus our main aim is to provide the best services to our customers. Our level of professionalism will become our barometer for customer satisfaction. We also aim to make it a point to have strong ties with our customers so we can grow the level of our professionalism and gain more trust among our clients.

Our Vision
Our dream is to become the one-stop shop for any kind of construction service that any of our clients need. We initially started with interlocking and asphalt paving, but we are now venturing into other services such as landscaping, pressure washing and sealing, concreting, decks and fences, demolition services and many more. We already have a wide range of service offerings, but we are not satisfied with just these. We are excited about every project that we perform and our possibilities for improvement and additional services are endless.

Our Commitment 
We commit to do whatever it takes to achieve the level of satisfaction our customer deserves. Our workmanship will leave a lasting mark and one that will be a reminder of our professionalism and close ties with our clients. We gained the trust of our customers through hard work that pays off when we see our clients happy with the outcome of our services. We will strive to be cooperative and readily available for any queries or requests our customer needs.

profile:
M.E. Contracting is one of Toronto's premier outdoor solutions companies. 

M.E. was Founded by owners Keren and Eitan Abu, with a desire to change the face of Toronto through the revitalization of outdoor living space. The “M” and “E” stand for Keren and Eitan's daughters, Mika and Emma. From the start these two girls have inspired the vision of innovation and creativity that M.E. embodies today. 

Specializing in custom landscape design, M.E. Contracting has spent over a decade executing this vision of innovation and construction. From decking to interlocking tile and pool building, M.E. Contracting differs from other Toronto landscapers through our commitment to excellence and attention to even the smallest of details. 

Want to see for yourself? Our 7,000 square foot landscaping showroom is the only showroom in Ontario dedicated to landscaping and outdoor transformations. Our exquisite showroom encapsulates features of all the custom design elements that every home owner dreams of having in their outdoor home space. In addition to the amazing  materials we have on display, our showroom includes an in-ground swimming pool with waterfalls, outdoor kitchens and outdoor furniture for prospective clients to experience.

Our vast experience in all aspects of landscaping design and construction has provided us with the ability to take on an array of projects, both varying in shape and size. Now matter what our goal to produce astounding and exceptional work remains unchanging. We aim to go above and beyond in our passion for what we do, and as a result we aim to surpass our client’s expectations with each and every element of landscaping design.

profile:
Canada’s Gardenland is a leading domestic landscape construction and maintenance service provider in the Greater Toronto area. Our team of lawn specialists utilizes their knowledge of lawn science and their skills of artistic application to create the perfect look for your specific landscaping scenario. We understand that each property and client taste is different so we work diligently with you and your surroundings to tailor the best approach for meeting those needs. Canada’s Gardenland has both the tools and the experience available to help you bring your landscaping dream to life.
Canada’s Gardenland designs, creates, maintains and provides tools for domestic landscaping projects in the Greater Toronto area. Both artistic landscaping skills and applied lawn science is utilized in order to achieve the perfect atmosphere and our professional team works closely with clients to ensure that projects meet specific needs and requirements.

Proper landscaping requires the application of various aspects in order to make your property look its best. Therefore, Canada’s Gardenland first helps with the design and creation of the right landscaping techniques that complement the natural lay of land as well as any man-made structures on the premises. We also offer a variety of interlocking stone techniques that provide landscaping accents through beautifully designed and applied walkways, driveways and patios.

We can also apply creative outdoor lighting effects so that your landscape is transformed into a stunning sight of beauty after dark and provides safety to those visiting after hours. Quality landscaping maintenance is also offered through sod fertilization, trimming, grooming, replanting and cleaning so that your property always looks its best.

profile:
Singular Focus:

Most landscape and renovation companies try to serve many types of customers at the same time; homeowners, shopping centers, office buildings, golf courses, and the list goes on. They are pulled in all directions trying to be everything to everyone. At Captain Handy Co, we focus on one customer, you, the homeowner. We have a singular focus on bringing you the best landscaping and interior renovation, the best customer service, and the best value for your home. When you consider that quality renovation can improve the value of your home by 10%-15%, why wouldn’t you hire the one company that focuses specifically on residential landscaping? We are Your Residential Landscape and interior renovation Company.
Easy:

Our business makes your life easier. We are committed to improving the quality of life for our customers so they can spend their time on other things. Our customers are busy and have hectic lives. They do not have time to deal with different companies for lawn care, mowing, design, patio building. Captain Handy Co. offers turn-key solutions to your landscape needs. One call connects you with one of our very qualified Landscape Advisors who will make sure that you are delighted with your landscape. It is that easy.
Hassle-Free:

Ever notice how some companies make it a hassle just to do business with them? Who needs hassles? Life is complicated enough as it is. With Captain Handy Co, you can expect fast response times, clear and concise proposals, and work to be done how and when we promise it would be. You can also expect us to stand behind our work, show up when we say we will and take care of the little things that can take a landscape,renovation and experience, from blah to wow! We take away the hassles so all you have to do is enjoy your landscape.
Professional:

With 5 years under our belts, we know a thing or two about being the professional contractor of choice. Our staff has an average tenure rate of over twelve years, and some team members have been with us for over two decades! They undergo extensive and on-going training to not only assure that your renovation looks fantastic, but also to make sure that you are treated superbly. Our staff members are clearly recognizable in their sharp uniforms so you will know who is on your property. With so many companies claiming to be “professional”, isn’t it nice to work with a company that actually is?
Our Values:

At Captain Handy Co, we provide Tender Loving Care to both you and your interior and landscape renovation. These are our Values:
•	Treat people honestly, fairly and with respect in all situations
•	Create a comfortable environment in which to work and do business
•	Be open to problems and complaints, and work quickly to a fair resolution
•	Present a professional image and working safely
•	Have a “can-do” attitude
•	Stand behind our commitment to quality and service
•	Be active, responsible and positive citizens in the communities in which we work

profile: ROYAL Decks Co. is a custom decking company priding itself in high quality of work and complete customer satisfaction. ROYAL Decks Co. focuses on specialty materials, such as exotic hardwoods, low maintenance materials and high grades of cedar. ROYAL Decks Co. offers a complete solution for a homeowner from custom designs to the execution of the project. ROYAL Decks Co. was founded in Burlington Ontario and quickly grew to serve all surrounding areas of Toronto and also Calgary since 2008 onwards. We are successful because we take every deck builder project as if it was the only one, although we build hundreds each year. Our success is based on the following five core values: Great design Quality work Build on time and budget Provide great warranty Safety Great design In order for the deck to be great, it has to be usable, look great and fulfill all of the customer's expectations. With our extensive experience, we will work with you to design the deck that will serve the purpose, according to your needs. This means getting the right size and shape of the deck, getting the right features and selecting the right materials. We work with many materials of different properties and we are sure to find one that will work for you. Build quality We have only the most experienced carpenters. Our carpenters have been in construction most of their lives and they build decks not because they have to, but because they love it. All of our decks have to meet very strict ROYAL Decks Co. quality control on top of any building code requirements. Our decks not only meet building code, they exceed it. Build on time and on budget Our estimate includes time frame when the project will be started, how long it will take and how much exactly it will cost. We strive to make the construction process an enjoyable experience. That is why we take these extra seriously. Provide great warranty We are proud to give one of the best warranties in the business to every deck that carries ROYAL Decks Co. name on it. We stand behind the work that we do. To see details about our warranty please visit our warranty website. Safety Safety is our utter most requirement doing any work. We carry both WCB and WSIB, to date without a single claim. We keep our workplace neat and organized to minimize any injuries. Sincerely, Miro

profile:
We Design, Construct and Maintain outdoor spaces that leave you breathless.

We are Ontario's leading landscaping and construction company, based in Toronto. We pride ourselves in providing professional, accurate and friendly service. We always assure 100% satisfaction to every customer, with quality work that lasts - for years and years of enjoyment.

We will help you with individual design ideas, materials, location recommendations & anything else needed, to get your landscaping project started.

All work is performed in an ethical and patient - yet timely - manner. And the quality is proudly guaranteed for up to 5 years.

profile:
Mr. Interlock Landscape & Construction is a professional residential and commercial design and build firm servicing the York Region and Greater Toronto Area communities.
 
With over 30 years of experience in interlocking and paving installations, we help our clients create a distinctive design element that will magnify their homes allure, increase its value while offering a unique look customized to meet their landscape desires.
 
We take pride in providing our clients with original and timeless designs, innovative ideas, quality construction, prompt and professional service, outstanding warranty and seamless flow of project implementation from start to finish.
 
Our construction expertise spans across a variety of materials from natural stone, flagstone, marble to cobblestones, standard pavers, concrete and asphalt.
 
We also specialize in a variety of project types such as driveways, patios, stairs, retaining walls, swimming pools, outdoor kitchenettes, outdoor living spaces, outdoor lighting, outdoor audio and more.
 
Our mission is to enhance and beautify the communities we enter by supplying our clients with a uniquely designed landscape project that adheres to our motto "Do It Once, Do It Right". All while providing our clients with unparalleled service through our consultation, planning and execution resulting in long lasting relationships and an abundance of word of mouth referrals.

profile:
Winner of many awards including a national and provincial award for best residential design. With passion and creativity and over twenty years' experience in beautifying properties all over the GTA, Land-Con prides itself on customer satisfaction and customer experience before, during and after the project is completed. We are very honest with our customers, keeping them up to date regularly with the progress of the project. We strive to give our customers the highest quality of work, starting with our very experienced in house, award winning landscape designers, as well as extremely professional and respectable trade personal on the job site, with the owners them selves over seeing every single project on a daily basis.
We have received industry wide recognition for design and build, professionalism and customer satisfaction.


ACCOMPLISHED TEAM
Active Member of Landscape Ontario and Bild.  ICPI and NCMA certified.  Techno-Bloc Pro installer.  Permacon Pro installer.  2016 Winner of 2 Landscape Awards of Excellence, 2017 winner of 3 landscape awards of excellence, 2019 National Award, 2020 Winner of 3 landscape awards of excellence and the Van Casey award for best Design. 
At Land-Con, our principles, passion and reputation speak for themselves.  Our valued clients will agree; excellence in project management, coupled with our highly qualified management and crew are second to none.


COMPASSIONATE CARE
We build to capture and reflect the unique vision our clients trust us to create while abiding to strict standards and timelines.  We value your expectations and opinion and respect the importance of budget guidelines.  The job site will always be left cleaned up and tidy and ready for next day construction.  We respect your property and will be courteous and considerate of you and your neighbors.


AFTER CARE
At Land-con we believe that after a project is completed the aftercare with our customers is just as important as any part of the project.  If at any time after the project is completed, you have any questions or concerns we are here to help.  We back our workmanship with a five year extended warranty.  This warranty is transferable if you happen to sell your home within the five year period.  Our top priority is customer service.  We take pride in providing courteous prompt responses to all clients past and current.

ABOUT THE OWNERS

Growing up together for the past 30 years, Ofer Winkler and Jeremy Lerner have formed a strong friendship which naturally became a great partnership.  They have both been in the landscape industry since 1997 giving each of them over 20 years experience in this industry.  Each one brings to the table their specialized onsite experience, and combined with their in class courses that they have attended over the years, makes them a team like no other.  Ofer and Jeremy have a passion for the landscape industry and each project they built over the years, which gives each home owner their own unique experience.  Their mission and vision is to give every home owner and project they build the attention and time they deserve.  This has made Land-Con a well-respected company by home owners, suppliers and even competitors around the GTA.  Together, they are an award winning team that transforms their clients' vision into reality, while providing professional services that meet the budget and time line.

profile:
Since we started serving the GTA in 2006 we have been dedicated to providing the ultimate finished product. We specialize in residential and commercial landscaping including Re/Re work such as trench and boulevard restoration. All of our work is designed to not only be aesthetically pleasing but also withstand the harsh Canadian climate. We also provide a complete property maintenance service for condo complexes, plazas, and residential. The end goal is to provide the best quality service to our clients. 

All jobs are fully insured and bonded. 

**

We provide helpful suggestions and create beautiful custom designs suitable for any budget. The sales representative's job isn't over after the contract is signed, they are there to help throughout the process, ready to answer any questions you might have and handle changes at the customers request in a professional and timely manner. Daily updates on how the project is going are provided to ensure that everything has been completed to our customers needs. We warranty all of our work. Our plan is to make sure that all of our customers enjoy working with us and enjoy their new outdoor space. 

**

Please contact us and we would be happy to send a sales representative out for a free quote with no obligation.

profile:
Outdoor Lighting Perspectives is the world's largest full-service outdoor lighting company, and we are proud to have our fixtures enjoyed at more than 150,000+ homes across North America. 

Whatever your outdoor lighting needs, we have the experience and expertise to get it done right the first time.

WHAT WE DO:

We want to transform your outdoor living spaces in the best way possible. Some of our exquisite outdoor lighting options include:

-Accent lighting to subtly show off your property’s best features
-Architectural lighting to highlight your home’s unique beauty
-Pool lighting to keep your nightly swims safe
-Patio and deck lights to add excitement to your nighttime entertaining
-Garden lighting to accentuate your stunning landscaping
-Path lighting to guide your guests where they need to go
-Up-lighting for home facade, trees, and outdoor artwork

From a single small garden that needs just a touch of light, to a sprawling estate home that needs lighting with zone control automation, we offer it all.

Call us today for a free at-home consultation, and one of our lighting designers will make a customs lighting design for your unique property.

WHAT MAKES US DIFFERENT:

We are dedicated outdoor lighting designers and installers. We do one thing, and we do it the best. We aren't a sprinkler company or lawn care company moonlighting in outdoor lights when times are slow. We will be here to take the call when your lights need maintenance years down the road.

We manufacture our lights by hand, mostly in the United States but some right here in Toronto, so we can control the entire chain of quality from raw materials to your beautiful garden. 

Our designers, installers, and service crews are all our own staff: we do not use sub-contractors. With Outdoor Lighting Perspectives, your satisfaction is guaranteed in writing and backed by our 30 year on-site warranty.

THE TRUSTWORTHY CHOICE:

How can you find an outdoor lighting contractor you can trust to get the work done right, on time, and safely? 

We have been independently vetted by a third-party for our complete and up-to-date liability insurance and workers compensation coverage, our safety and training compliance, and our long established track record of happy customer referrals and testimonials. 

Companies claiming to do lighting come and go, but we're celebrating 20 years and our warranty is backed by our international network of 60+ locations. We'll install your lights today, but we'll also maintain them for years to come.

THE NEXT STEP:

We offer free design consultations and free quotes. Please contact us to discuss your outdoor lighting needs and how we can be of assistance.

profile:
Design Turf has a 20-year history of selling ProGreen artificial grass products in the GTA and beyond. Our residential grass series has a brown fiber thatch producing a realistic looking grass and is 33% cooler than conventional turf. Plus, with the new patent-pending ProFlow backing that increases the drainage rate by approximately 400% and our moisture resistant fibers, the turf will be cleaner, drier and free from any unpleasant pet odors. Design Turf is also recognized for offering the highest quality of golf green products & for their professional installations. Design Turf golf greens are priced at $30/ft²+HST for full installation. A small 12’x15’, 2 hole backyard golf green can be as little as $7500+HST complete! 
 
Our most popular selling landscape turf averages $19/ft²+HST for full installation. All our turf is pet friendly and has excellent drainage! 
 
ProGreen manufacturing is the only North American artificial grass manufacturer to produce their products under one roof from start to finish. Our products are certifiably 100% LEAD & HEAVY METAL FREE!  ProGreen products have a life expectancy of 30-40 years, even under the harshest of conditions, including the play of multiple dogs or when used by busy daycare centers!
 
For the Do-It-Yourselfer
Design Turf’s price on Natural Prime 50 for supply only is just $6.20/ft²+HST (remember it supplied only and the rolls are 15' wide!). Find out how to install it yourself here!
 
Please contact us! Provide a daytime phone number, email address and street address, we ’ll be happy to show you samples and arrange a free quotation.

profile: Algonquin Property Services Inc is a family-owned, full-service landscaping company that has been in operation since 1997. The owners, Steve and Samantha Bell, have always had a love for nature and the outdoors. The company’s name was inspired by one of their favourite Canadian parks. Their hope is to convey the tranquil feeling of being in nature on your own property. Starting with a staff of only three in the landscaping and snow removal business, the company has now grown to a staff of over 30.  As a family-run company, their three children have grown up with the business and have naturally absorbed the skills. Learning through hands-on experience and through studying horticulture at Humber College, they have fallen in love with this rewarding industry and are excited to continue to grow. We are specialized in landscape maintenance, landscape construction, snow removal, and window cleaning jobs. We provide property services in Durham Region and the GTA. Contact us.

profile:
Landscaping Contractors & Designers, Interlocking Stone.

OWNERSHIP AND CREDENTIALS
Hofstetter Landscaping is owned and operated by Rick and Ashleigh Hofstetter. Our “baby” was born in 1989 and is now 23 years old. (In case you’re wondering how old we are...suffices to say we are evergreens. :-)  Did we tell you we are a landscaping company?) 
From the beginning, we have always endeavoured to do the best quality work possible for our clients. We specialize in landscaping and that’s one of the reasons our “baby” has no siblings—no sister companies, no associates, no partners, no branches. Landscaping is what we do and we do it really well.

A TORONTO LANDSCAPING COMPANY WITH A DIFFERENCE
Ever since we started, and even more so now, we find the market exploding with Toronto landscaping companies that make a big noise about “cheap, cheap”. Now, if they were selling birds, it would be okay, but they are not, right? And yet, we often lose a job to a cheap company that “specializes” in being a “Jack-of-all-trades”. Do we want to compete with them? No. But does that mean we are frightfully expensive? Not at all! In fact, our goal is always to ensure that our customers get the best value for money and a landscape that makes them the envy of the neighbourhood without breaking the bank.

As we come across customers who do their due diligence by comparing quotes, we are very mindful and respectful of the fact that one needs to be price conscious. It’s when we are told about a competitive quote that implies “the other guy” can get the job done for less than it costs us to buy quality materials, the alarm bells go off. He needs a hefty deposit from you to pay his guys for the last job done, and of course, there is always that famous curbside taillight guarantee!

We would like to go on and tell you what we have learned and found out in these past 23 years but you wouldn't be able to read it all...

WHY YOU SHOULD CHOOSE TO ENGAGE OUR LANDSCAPING SERVICES IN TORONTO 

All we want to say is this—we do top quality work with a guarantee you can count on, every single time. If it’s not to your liking we'll do what it takes to make it right. We'll be there in years to come, particularly if the weather has given the work a beating. 

•	We are fully covered with 5 million liability insurance and WSIB approved. 
•	Our crew is safety certified or they don't work for us. 
•	Our business has City of Toronto licensing.
•	Each team member has government ID.
•	We pay our taxes and are an ethical, honest, law-abiding enterprise.

Yes, you will find cheaper Toronto landscaping companies out there. Will you find one better than us in terms of reputation for quality work and customer references? Not likely. 

Please visit our website (www.HofstetterLandscaping.com) or call us today at 647-955-8382 to book a free, no obligation landscaping consultation in Toronto.

profile:
Bestloc Interlocking is trusted and respected landscape design and Installation company operating in the Greater Toronto and Surrounding Areas. As a proud and certified member of ICPI (Interlocking and Concrete Pavement Institute), we provide our clients with award winning landscape designs and industry leading installations. Bestloc was found on two main principles of encouraging family outdoor living and building structures that last.

Many years ago, Ryan Morant, founder and president started out being a labourer, where he developed his passion for the trade. He then became a foreman, and inspector, and subsequently a teacher. Under his leadership, our professional team of highly skilled and qualified personnel provides innovative landscape designs. With over 15 years of planting and masonry experience, and hundreds of thousands of square feet laid, Bestloc Interlocking embodies the values of strength, performance, and passion. We are dedicated to providing our clients with custom landscaping solutions.

We are in constant communication with our friends at ICPI (Interlocking and Concrete Pavement Institute), and are always up-to-date on industry leading techniques on landscape designs and installations. We offer good communication with our clients from the beginning of each project to its completion. Our experienced project management means your project is completed on time and on budget.

Furthermore, we complete every task with a commitment to integrity and a devotion to excellence using the best quality products guaranteed to leave a lasting impression. If you wish to create the finest outdoor living experience for you and your family, please do not hesitate to contact Bestloc Interlocking for a free consultation/estimate.

profile:
Landscaping Contractors & Designers, Interlocking Stone.

OWNERSHIP AND CREDENTIALS
Hofstetter Landscaping is owned and operated by Rick and Ashleigh Hofstetter. Our “baby” was born in 1989 and is now 23 years old. (In case you’re wondering how old we are...suffices to say we are evergreens. :-)  Did we tell you we are a landscaping company?) 
From the beginning, we have always endeavoured to do the best quality work possible for our clients. We specialize in landscaping and that’s one of the reasons our “baby” has no siblings—no sister companies, no associates, no partners, no branches. Landscaping is what we do and we do it really well.

A TORONTO LANDSCAPING COMPANY WITH A DIFFERENCE
Ever since we started, and even more so now, we find the market exploding with Toronto landscaping companies that make a big noise about “cheap, cheap”. Now, if they were selling birds, it would be okay, but they are not, right? And yet, we often lose a job to a cheap company that “specializes” in being a “Jack-of-all-trades”. Do we want to compete with them? No. But does that mean we are frightfully expensive? Not at all! In fact, our goal is always to ensure that our customers get the best value for money and a landscape that makes them the envy of the neighbourhood without breaking the bank.

As we come across customers who do their due diligence by comparing quotes, we are very mindful and respectful of the fact that one needs to be price conscious. It’s when we are told about a competitive quote that implies “the other guy” can get the job done for less than it costs us to buy quality materials, the alarm bells go off. He needs a hefty deposit from you to pay his guys for the last job done, and of course, there is always that famous curbside taillight guarantee!

We would like to go on and tell you what we have learned and found out in these past 23 years but you wouldn't be able to read it all...

WHY YOU SHOULD CHOOSE TO ENGAGE OUR LANDSCAPING SERVICES IN TORONTO 

All we want to say is this—we do top quality work with a guarantee you can count on, every single time. If it’s not to your liking we'll do what it takes to make it right. We'll be there in years to come, particularly if the weather has given the work a beating. 

•	We are fully covered with 5 million liability insurance and WSIB approved. 
•	Our crew is safety certified or they don't work for us. 
•	Our business has City of Toronto licensing.
•	Each team member has government ID.
•	We pay our taxes and are an ethical, honest, law-abiding enterprise.

Yes, you will find cheaper Toronto landscaping companies out there. Will you find one better than us in terms of reputation for quality work and customer references? Not likely. 

Please visit our website (www.HofstetterLandscaping.com) or call us today at 647-955-8382 to book a free, no obligation landscaping consultation in Toronto.

Willowtree Construction Company's founder Frank Samifanni started undertaking renovation projects as a sole proprietor in 1997. Frank's philosophy in delivering quality work and that has earned him positive and solid reviews and a strong referral base. In 2007 Frank incorporated his company under Willowtree Construction Company and went full force as a General Contractor. 

Presently Willowtree Construction Company undertakes mid size to large size projects from design/ build custom built homes, additions and extensions to the existing structure, complete home renovation including kitchen, bathroom and basement renovations to structural changes . 
As a general Contracting company our trained and licensed trades carry on the work assigned with full professionalism and promptness. We love to deliver turn key projects.

profile:
HENRY'S BOBCAT SERVICE
Our services include excavation/digging, back filling, water main breaks, landscaping, concrete work and breaking, post holes and more.

We supply you with experienced operators and the equipment you need on your project at reasonable rates.

We provide bobcats, excavators, track machines, backhoes and other machines along with the necessary equipment required for most residential and industrial projects.

Materials such as sand, gravel, topsoil, sod and any boxes/bins required for the cleanup of waste or dirt removal can also be supplied.

profile:
We would like to take this opportunity to introduce ourselves.  We are Pristine Property Maintenance Limited (PPM) and we undertake grounds and snow\ice maintenance contracts in the GTA, Kawarthas and Eastern Ontario.  We are a mid-sized company that has years of experience in the industry and are currently seeking additional properties to commence this Spring.  Our focus and expertise lies largely in the grounds and snow\ice maintenance for condominium townhomes; however, we also have a wealth of experience in high-rise and commercial complexes.

We work around the clock to establish a name for ourselves – we believe strongly that this comes only with hard work and loyalty to our customers.  In response to our successes thus far, we continue to strive to meet our goal to expand PPM into every facet of the industry.  

Our standard contracts include grass cutting and trimming, aeration, garden maintenance, three fertilizing applications per year, tree\hedge\shrub trimming, litter and debris removal, full spring and fall clean-ups, snow clearing\removal operations, and ice control.  We are also contracted for additional services such as irrigation system maintenance, tree\annual flowers\shrub installations, tree maintenance, changing light bulbs within the premises, cleaning eavestroughs, installing\removing holiday lights, removing\collecting garbage and bulk junk, asphalt repairs and blacktopping, or line painting – to name a few.

We look forward to working with you!

profile:
Aventus Landscaping is a premier award winning residential landscape construction firm that has been servicing the Toronto and Greater Toronto communities since 2010.  We are a complete landscape design and build company specializing in outdoor living spaces with the simple objective of beautifying the neighbourhoods we work in. 

We have a hands-on approach to our project deliverables as we personally oversee every project detail ensuring our outcome meets our gold standard of quality.  After all:  your  goal is our goal – to design and build a dream landscaping project be it for functionality or entertainment purposes our commitment to excellence remains the same.  

Our landscape designers take pride in finding creative and unique approaches to landscaping that not only beautify your property, but do so in a cost efficient way. Whether your intentions are to create a ‘staycation’ escape, a more comfortable outdoor entertaining area or a low maintenance approach to help keep up with your busy lifestyle our team will work with you by understanding your needs and creating a personalized landscape design that accommodates. 

We are always looking forward to servicing new clients.

profile:
Today quality of service and personal attention are lacking in the landscape and outdoor living industries. With Krava Home Services you will receive extensive experience and a track record of quality with our property maintenance, landscape design and installation, and outdoor living construction throughout Toronro. Our team of experts will ensure your unique outdoor living area will maintain beauty, health and longevity. We are eager to preserve the beauty of your property – from a town home complex, private home, or business.
 
You want a company that has vision and experience for your landscapes design, and Krava Home Services has the planning and construction expertise needed to for your home’s project around GTA & Vaughn cities. Whether just a low maintenance landscape with a simple water feature or a full blown outdoor living area with a patio, driveways, and more, we will devote as much care and attention to your project as needed. We offer design advice for smaller jobs, as well as complete site plans for larger landscaping projects. If you’re planning a landscape project around Toronto, large or small, give us a call. We will be happy to listen to you and help anyway we can. You can be sure we will be committed to the creation of a unique, long lasting, outdoor living area for your home.
 
A beautifully designed patio makes spring and summer in the Garden State even sweeter. While flowers and foliage bring bright pops up color to your landscape, a patio adds an extra dimension of comfort, both aesthetically and functionally. Krava Home Services is one of the most trusted patio construction contractors in Toronto. Our patio service includes building everything from small custom outdoor patio designs to grand garden paths.

profile:
Stoneworks Landscape Inc. has served residential clients in Toronto, Markham, Richmond Hill and Vaughan, since 1995.  We offer Complete Landscape Design & Build Services.  Our crews are highly skilled, efficient and courteous.  We use the best equipment to help us with our projects.   All our work is fully guaranteed.

   All projects start with a detailed proposal outlining the scope and cost.   Our team of experienced personnel  work closely with clients through every stage of the design & construction process to ensure  creative & unique outdoor solutions.   Our projects are always delivered on time and on budget.

We build the right way from the ground up.  Our above standard site preparation ensures our work looks great for years to come.  We use “Grade A” gravel materials, properly compacted, as a foundation to all paved areas.   All gardens start with a healthy amount of high quality Triple Mix Soil.   All natural materials such as plants, rocks and flagstones are carefully hand selected to ensure integrity of the specimen.

profile:
Toronto Landscaping Contractor

Merlin Landscape Construction is an outdoor design and build landscape contracting company in Toronto. Believing that form follows function our team of landscape professionals applies real world knowledge to each project.

Designed to Fit

One of our top priorities is to educate our clients. Industry standard installation procedures and proper material selection are paramount to any successful landscape renovation.

Landscaping Tip:

Possibly one of the most prevalent mistakes homeowners make is to take on their landscape a little at a time. They start projects, begin to clear areas add a mix of plants and continue without a plan. The outcome is a mishmash of plantings and gardens that give the property a disorganized feel. Implementing a design plan with a prepared budget will lead a homeowner to a beautiful landscape that they can feel good about.

Get in touch with Merlin Landscape Construction today to start your landscape plan. Visit Online @ MerlinConstruction.ca or Call 416 880 0151 or 647-328-9840

If you're in need of Concrete / Asphalt paving for your driveway at home, a scenic interlocking stone walkway for your home/business or parking lot paving for industrial use, you can trust the services of N.P Construction / Renovation and Landscaping LTD.

profile: Landscaping services are a valuable investment in your home that will raise your property value when done properly by a professional. Landscaping Huntingdon PA is a company you can count on to deliver outstanding results. We have been in the business for years, and recently decided to form our own company so we can better meet the needs of our clients. We are you one stop shop for your landscaping needs. We are able to work with you to create a total site plan to optimize your layout providing the most bang for your buck while also keeping the most pleasing aesthetic aspects of high end landscaping. We are experts in laying down paver patios and walkways to help set boundaries and provide easy walking access to houses, decks, pools, etc... We also construct retaining walls to help divert water runoff and provide flat usable space where there might not otherwise be. If you are looking for raised beds or accent gardens we are also very knowledgeable and can help you choose complimentary plants that will not only look great all season but require minimal maintenance. We also provide lawn services for small and large lots, commercial and residential, with the attention to detail you would expect from professional landscaping experts. In the off season we specialize in snow removal for commercial and residential clients. We are able to plow and shovel snow off sidewalks, driveways, parking lots, and anywhere else it is not wanted.
